!CCCC          READ DELIMITER IS SPECIFIED, SPACES WILL NOT BE TREATED
!CCCC          AS DELIMITERS FOR CHARACTER FIELDS.  THIS WAS DONE SINCE
!CCCC          MANY COMMA DELIMITED FILES ALLOW SPACES IN CHARACTER
!CCCC          FIELDS.  HOWEVER, THIS MEANS THAT SETTING THE COMMA AS
!CCCC          A DEFAULT DELIMITER CREATES PROBLEMS FOR FILES THAT ARE
!CCCC          NOT ACTUALLY COMMA DELIMITED (E.G., CHARACTER FIELDS ARE
!CCCC          DELIMITED WITH SPACES OR TABS).
