       CON4, CON5, CV, DA, DAI, DAJN, DAJP, DAK1, DAK2, DAK3, DB, EC,   &
       E1, E2, FPI12, F1, F2, RTRX, RX, SCV, T, TEMP1, TEMP2, TT, X
      DIMENSION AJP(19), AJN(19), A(15), B(15)
      DIMENSION AK1(14), AK2(23), AK3(14)
