!                  DOUBLE SAMPLE ACCEPTANCE PLAN P1 P2 ALPHA BETA (NOT WORKING)
!
!                  K MEANS CLUSTER Y1 TO YK                    (HLR)
!                  NORMAL MIXTURE CLUSTER Y1 TO YK             (HLR)
!                  K MEDOIDS CLUSTER Y1 TO YK
!                  FUZZY CLUSTER Y1 TO YK
!                  AGNES CLUSTER Y1 TO YK
!                     (SINGLE LINKAGE, COMPLETE LINKAGE,
!                      AVERAGE LINKAGE, CENTROID LINKAGE,
!                      WARD'S LINKAGE, WEIGHTED AVERAGE LINKAGE,
!                      GOWER'S LINKAGE)
!                  DIANA CLUSTER Y1 TO YK
!
!     WRITTEN BY--JAMES J. FILLIBEN
!                 STATISTICAL ENGINEERING DIVISION
!                 INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY LABORATORY
!                 NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STANDARDS AND TECHNOLOGY
!                 GAITHERSBURG, MD 20899-8980
!                 PHONE--301-975-2855
!     NOTE--DATAPLOT IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK
!           OF THE NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STANDARDS AND TECHNOLOGY.
!     LANGUAGE--ANSI FORTRAN (1977)
!     VERSION NUMBER--82.6
!     ORIGINAL VERSION--JANUARY   1981.
!     UPDATED         --MARCH     1981.
!     UPDATED         --JULY      1981.
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    1981.
!     UPDATED         --SEPTEMBER 1981.
!     UPDATED         --OCTOBER   1981.
!     UPDATED         --NOVEMBER  1981.
!     UPDATED         --MARCH     1982.
!     UPDATED         --MAY       1982.
!     UPDATED         --JULY      1987. YATES ANALYSIS
!     UPDATED         --FEBRUARY  1988. LOWESS FIT
